title: Anke Domscheit-Berg
snippet: Anke Domscheit-Berg was a member of Alliance 90/The Greens in the Mitte borough of Berlin.[14] In May 2012 she joined the Pirate Party Germany.[15] From August 2013 to July 2014, Domscheit-Berg was chair of the Pirate Party in Brandenburg.[16]
